{"tid":2250331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美最高法院 允許賓夕法尼亞州點算大選日後三天內郵寄選票","createTime":"2020-10-20T04:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T06:49:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12747ff02381625496c3376ff641d6355878e671","tid":2250331,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"美國最高法院拒絕應共和黨人要求推翻下級法院裁決，決定繼續允許賓夕法尼亞州，點算在大選日後三天內寄到的郵寄選票。判決被指對支持郵寄投票的民主黨人有利。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在上屆大選在賓夕法尼亞州勝出，但今屆民調顯示落後於民主黨對手拜登。 <br />\n<br />\n大法官金斯伯格去世後，最高法院的保守和開明大法官比例為「5對3」，今次裁決是因保守派的首席大法官羅伯茨「倒戈」。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，假如國會通過巴雷特出任最高法院大法官的提名，未來在大選相關的判案中，保守派會有決定性影響。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2362387&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=30928413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362387</a>"},{"pid":"0f3bae5bd837a063468d23c84d4dd3e62bf97f8f","tid":2250331,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"選後先寄<br />\n造幾多票都duck"},{"pid":"2f42bd345f456db649d9033a07b3dffe5be6a4bf","tid":2250331,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"登登冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302cdd544be73dac0b6de48e86a5013121aa0d53","tid":2250331,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd36ab6319b915bce9e0ae3240f0a9a9f955dc3","tid":2250331,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"Trump可以放棄賓州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji